{"tid":2418191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有相︱鄭若驊麒麟臂鬥葉劉天蠶腿","createTime":"2021-02-22T12:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T13:54:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"57cc80279d32359b78d47f1244b4342b82ebef0d","tid":2418191,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s4gT01YxIZLrHNdHgfkTEPfMGeI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4L7VALHS4VAC5E6GPDBEYACJXE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs4gT01YxIZLrHNdHgfkTEPfMGeI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4L7VALHS4VAC5E6GPDBEYACJXE.png&h=e0fadeba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥帶頭打香港第一針武肺疫苗，好多市民都注視佢有咩反應。其他高官司局長亦輪流上陣；多名行政會議成員，包括葉劉淑儀、李國章等，都率先感受國家嘅愛。立法會主席梁君彥話，首批接種疫苗嘅議員係「義勇軍」同「白老鼠」！<br />\n<br />\n至於中國科興疫苗有幾好？睇吓佢哋就知道。葉劉一雙肉腿，在場內輕易成為焦點；不過，當鄭若驊展示麒麟臂接受注射，展示出十足嘅實力嘅時候，立即搶晒fo。呢一次，鄭若驊贏番次！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/HSGYZFX2QVFCNB7732XACYQSSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FHSGYZFX2QVFCNB7732XACYQSSY%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=684865d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FHSGYZFX2QVFCNB7732XACYQSSY%2F&h=b4ebc1cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/HSGYZFX2QVFCNB7732XACYQSSY/</a>"},{"pid":"1ad41e177cd184e8da40c0b3026a4adecc6888be","tid":2418191,"uid":354682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不能只有我睇到"},{"pid":"780e722c90e6c175833a7cfe62f223a5d8e10bc0","tid":2418191,"uid":40010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:1